Defines what the role is allowed to do
 Grants least-privilege access to the private bucket

⚠ Replace your-private-bucket-unique-001

{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "PrivateBucketAccess",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "s3:ListBucket"
      ],
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::your-private-bucket-unique-001"
    },
    {
      "Sid": "PrivateObjectAccess",
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": [
        "s3:GetObject",
        "s3:PutObject"
      ],
      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::your-private-bucket-unique-001/*"
    }
  ]
}


✔ Security purpose: restricts access to one bucket only
✔ No wildcard permissions
✔ Supports upload, download, listing
